nd-Stefanie-Keenan_The-Hollywood-Reporter-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rachel-chinouriri">雷切尔·钦鲁里（Rachel Chinouriri）</a>分享了她对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adele">阿黛尔（Adele）</a>的反应，为英国奖提名发送了鲜花。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-rachel-chinouriri-interview-what-a-devastating-turn-of-events-3570580">Rachel Chinouriri终于回家了</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">2025年仪式的提名人于周四（1月23日）揭幕</a>，Chinouriri收到了年度艺术家和最佳新艺术家的点头。这是在2024年发行她的首张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/rachel-chinouriri-what-a-devastating-turn-of-events-review-radar-3752098">What a a a毁灭性事件</a>》之后。</p><p>在祝贺她的人中，有英国人学校校友阿黛尔（Adele），他向前<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/rachel-chinouriri-15-01-2024-3570580"><em>NME</em>封面明星</a>送了一束粉红色的玫瑰，并写了一张纸条，上面写着：“祝贺您的英国人提名Rachel。我为您感到高兴，迫不及待想参加演出！爱，阿黛尔。”</p><p>为了对交货的反应，Chinouriri上了Twitter/X写道：“帮助我如何从中恢复过来”，并补充说：“我摇晃……剧烈。”</p><p>她继续在Instagram上说：“我知道这东西有时对其他艺术家来说并不重要，但是我认为因为我去了英国学校，我记得看到阿黛尔站在舞台上，她就像，&#39;我曾经像你一样，当她表演时。</p><p>她说：“她指着一点，我在坑里。” “我记得像，哇，真是太酷了 - 不过，我永远无法做到。”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">谢谢阿黛尔<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f62d.png" alt="😭" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/FhsKpQojNe">pic.twitter.com/fhskpqojne</a></p><p> - 雷切尔（@RachelChinourir） <a href="https://twitter.com/rachelchinourir/status/1882777316784476471?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年1月24日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>这不是阿黛尔第一次对Chinouriri表示钦佩。在去年在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-extends-las-vegas-residency-with-32-more-shows-3518855">拉斯维加斯居住的“周末与阿黛尔的周末”</a>演出中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-shouts-out-amazing-rachel-chinouriri-during-vegas-residency-3585975">她告诉人群</a>：“有一位新艺术家，她是英国人，她的名字是雷切尔（Rachel），她确实喜欢独立音乐。”然后她补充说：“她绝对很棒，她在三月份在洛杉矶举行一场演出，我将独自一人去。那就是我要做的。”</p><p> Chinouriri在今年早些时候发布了她的首张唱片《多么毁灭性的事件》。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/rachel-chinouriri-what-a-devastating-turn-of-events-review-radar-3752098">四星级的评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>说：“尽管有一些令人震惊的事件”，尽管它的冠军略带令人震惊，但它一直很迷人，同时提供了足够的声音和范围，以暗示Chinouriri的未来野心。她努力工作，听起来很容易。</p><p> The record was named one of <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-debut-albums-2024-3818990"><em>NME</em> &#39;s 20 Best Debut Albums of 2024</a> , and came in at Number 10 in our overall <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995">50 Best Albums of 2024 list</a> . </p><figure id="attachment_3819014" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3819014" style="width: 1200px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3819014" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/RACHEL-CHINOURIRI@1200x1200.jpg" alt="Rachel Chinouriri ‘What A Devastating Turn Of Events’ album artwork, photo by press" width="1200" height="1200" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/RACHEL-CHINOURIRI@1200x1200.jpg 1200w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/RACHEL-CHINOURIRI@1200x1200-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/RACHEL-CHINOURIRI@1200x1200-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/RACHEL-CHINOURIRI@1200x1200-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/RACHEL-CHINOURIRI@1200x1200-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/RACHEL-CHINOURIRI@1200x1200-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3819014" class="wp-caption-text"> Credit: Press</figcaption></figure><p> Later this year, Chinouriri will serve as opening support for <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpente