er</a> – is shortlisted for Mastercard Album Of The Year.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rachel-chinouriri-reacts-after-adele-sends-her-flowers-following-brit-awards-nominations-shaking-3831948">Rachel Chinouriri reacts after Adele sends her flowers following BRIT Awards nominations: “Shaking”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
