68x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> DJ Unk, the Atlanta rapper remembered for his &#39;00s hits &#39;Walk It Out&#39; and &#39;2 Step&#39;, has died at the age of 42.</p><p> The news was confirmed by his wife Sherkita Long-Platt on social media on Friday (January 24), although no cause of death has yet been confirmed.</p><p> “Please respect me and my family,” Long-Platt wrote on Facebook. “我只是失去了丈夫，孩子们刚失去了父亲。我们的生活永远不会一样。我永远爱你安东尼。”</p><p> The artist, real name Anthony Leonard Platt, began his career as a teenager in Atlanta in 1998 as part of the Southern Style DJs crew, before signing with Big Oomp Records where he broke out as a solo artist.</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> RIP to DJ Unk, the “Walk It Out” creator has sadly passed away at 42, confirmed by his family in several emotional IG posts. <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/RIP?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#RIP</a> <a href="https://t.co/0BNm5NbFur">pic.twitter.com/0BNm5NbFur</a></p><p> — Glock Topickz (@Glock_Topickz) <a href="https://twitter.com/Glock_Topickz/status/1882934663943168201?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 24, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Considered a key figure in snap music, a subgenre of crunk, he scored major hits in 2006 with &#39;Walk It Out&#39; and &#39;2 Step&#39;, the former reaching the Top Ten on the Billboard Hot 100 and spawning a remix featuring <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andre-3000">Andre 3000</a> . Both songs were included on Unk&#39;s debut album &#39;Beat&#39;n Down Yo Block!&#39; in the same year, which included features from the likes of Baby Dand Jazze Pha. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Unk - Walk It Out" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/O05S7ZLPbEw?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> His second studio album &#39;2econd Season&#39; was released in 2008, before he suffered a heart attack in 2009, something he attributed to “not exercising and not eating right”. His output reduced after the health scare, although he did release the album &#39;Fresh Off Dem Papers&#39; in 2017.</p><p> Big Oomp Records的一位代表向UNK致敬：“我们以沉重的心和深刻的悲伤宣布，我们宣布了一个真正的ATL传奇人物，Anthony Platt，安东尼·普拉特（Anthony Platt）更加称为&#39;dj unk&#39;。”</p><p> “ DJ UNK不仅是传奇的DJ，说唱歌手和制作人，而且是我们标签的真正基石，以及他留下的烙印将永远珍惜。”</p><p> UNK的最后一次重大露面是在2023年的BET奖中，他作为混合泳的一部分进行了“走出去”，还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soulja-boy">Soulja Boy</a>和Fly</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/walk-it-out-rapper-dj-unk-has-died-aged-42-3831949">“ Walk It Out”说唱歌手DJ Unk去世了，现年42岁的</a>NME出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
